/Oliver-Stone-and-Ryan-Gosling-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Oliver-Stone-and-Ryan-Gosling-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Oliver-Stone-and-Ryan-Gosling-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oliver-stone">奥利弗·斯通 (Oliver Stone)</a>表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-gosling">瑞恩·高斯林 (Ryan Gosling)</a>拍摄<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>《芭比娃娃》</em></a>这样的电影是在“浪费时间”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019">《芭比娃娃》评论：格蕾塔·葛韦格的成人玩具故事非常有趣</a></strong></li></ul><p>高斯林在去年<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/greta-gerwig">格蕾塔·葛韦格 (Greta Gerwig)</a>的热门电影中扮演肯一角，赢得了广泛好评，包括最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/baftas-2024-nominations-see-the-full-list-3572944">获得英国电影和电视艺术学院 (BAFTA) 男配角提名</a>。</p><p>然而，曾执导过<em>《野战排》</em>和<em>《刺杀肯尼迪</em>》等电影的斯通去年在接受<a href="https://www.cityam.com/oliver-stone-on-vladimir-putin-nuclear-power-and-being-an-outsider/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>City AM</em></a>采访时批评了这部电影，并猛烈抨击了美泰老板关于他可以执导<em>芭比娃娃</em>续集的“荒谬”笑话建议。</p><p> “如果瑞恩·高斯林为了钱而做这种事，那他就是在浪费时间，”斯通补充道。 “他应该拍更严肃的电影。他不应该成为好莱坞幼稚化的一部分。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="芭比 |主要预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pBk4NYhWNMM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “现在全是幻想、幻想、幻想，包括所有战争图片：幻想、幻想。就连我以前喜欢的《<em>速度与激情</em>》也变得像漫威电影了。我的意思是，你能看到多少次车祸？”</p><p>在采访中，斯通还把矛头指向了<em>《疾速追杀》</em>系列电影，他回忆起最近的一次飞行：“所以在飞机上我看了<em>《疾速追杀》</em> ，看了三个多小时。期间我睡着了大约 778 次。我不断地醒来，不得不面对他杀死更多的人。就好像世界已经堕落到没有逻辑了。”</p><p>斯通以直言不讳而闻名，这位导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/film/oliver-stone-says-hollywood-has-gone-mad-its-like-an-alice-in-wonderland-tea-party-2707947">早在 2020 年 COVID-19 大流行期间就批评了好莱坞</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3574967" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3574967" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3574967" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Oliver-Stone-2023.jpg" alt="奥利弗·斯通" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Oliver-Stone-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Oliver-Stone-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Oliver-Stone-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Oliver-Stone-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Oliver-Stone-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Oliver-Stone-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3574967" class="wp-caption-text">导演奥利弗·斯通于 2023 年 12 月 2 日在意大利都灵举行的 2023 年第 41 届都灵电影节期间出席奥利弗·斯通电影《核现在》的媒体拍照活动。图片来源：Getty / Stefano Guidi</figcaption></figure><p> “营销成本太高了，”他告诉<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/07/13/magazine/oliver-stone-interview.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><em>《纽约时报》杂志</em></a>。 “一切都变得太脆弱、太敏感。现在的好莱坞——没有新冠病毒顾问就无法拍电影。没有敏感性顾问，你就无法拍电影。这太荒谬了。”</p><p>他补充道：“学院每五个月、十个月、两个月就会改变一次关于它想要跟上的事情的想法。这在政治上是正确的，而且这不是我急于进入的世界。我从来没有见过它如此疯狂。这就像<em>爱丽丝梦游仙境的</em>茶会。”</p><p>与此同时，高斯林<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ryan-goslings-bemused-reaction-to-barbie-song-im-just-ken-winning-critics-choice-award-has-gone-viral-3570997">上周因《I&#39;m Just Ken》获得评论家选择奖“最佳原创歌曲”奖而震惊不已，引起了广泛关注</a>。</p><p>瑞恩·高斯林 (Ryan Gosling) 认为奥利弗·斯通 (Oliver Stone) 首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ryan-gosling-is-wasting-his-time-making-films-like-barbie-argues-oliver-stone-3574949">，他认为制作《芭比娃娃》这样的电影是在“浪费时间”</a> 。</p> ;
 Spotify猛烈抨击苹果“令人发指”的新计划，并指责他们为保护利润“不择手段” https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-slam-apples-outrageous-new-plans-and-accuse-them-of-stopping-at-nothing-to-protect-profits-3574954?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=spotify-slam-apples-令人发指的新计划并指责他们不惜一切代价保护利润Will RichardsMon, 22 Jan 2024 14:55:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsAppleSpotify https://www.nme.com/?p=3574954 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/spotify-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Spotify" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/spotify-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/spotify-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/spotify-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/spotify-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/spotify-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/spotify-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这些费用将向在 Apple Store 以外销售产品的开发者收取</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-slam-apples-outrageous-new-plans-and-accuse-them-of-stopping-at-nothing-to-protect-profits-3574954">Spotify 抨击苹果“令人发指”的新计划，并指责他们为保护利润“不择手段”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/spotify-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Spotify" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/spotify-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/spotify-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/spotify-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/spotify-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/spotify-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/spotify-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/spotify">Spotify</a>猛烈抨击了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple">苹果</a>提高交易费用的新计划，称其“令人愤慨”。</p><p>根据新计划，苹果将向在 Apple Store 以外销售产品的应用开发商收取高达 27% 的佣金。</p><p>对此，Spotify 指责该公司为保护利润“不择手段”，并敦促英国政府防止类似情况在英国发生。</p><p>这些费用是在与<em>《堡垒之夜</em>》开发商 Epic Games 发生法律纠纷后推出的。它允许人们绕过苹果系统订阅服务，但向他们收取高达 27% 的佣金。目前，最大的开发商使用苹果系统需要支付 30% 的费用，但 85% 的开发商则无需支付任何费用。</p><p> Spotify 在谈到这一裁决时表示：“苹果再次证明，他们将不惜一切代价保护他们在应用程序商店垄断下从开发者和消费者那里获取的利润”，并声称它“公然公然”创建市场竞争更加激烈。 </p><figure id="attachment_3571761" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3571761" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3571761" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Spotify-stock-image.jpg" alt="这张插图照片于 2023 年 12 月 5 日在波兰克拉科夫拍摄，手机屏幕上显示耳机和 Spotify 标志。（摄影：Jakub Porzycki/NurPhoto via Getty Images）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Spotify-stock-image.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Spotify-stock-image-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Spotify-stock-image-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Spotify-stock-image-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Spotify-stock-image-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Spotify-stock-image-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3571761" class="wp-caption-text">这张插图照片于 2023 年 12 月 5 日在波兰克拉科夫拍摄，手机屏幕上显示耳机和 Spotify 标志。（摄影：Jakub Porzycki/NurPhoto via Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>关于英国类似系统的潜力，Spotify 补充道：“英国的数字市场、竞争和消费者法案必须结束这种虚假姿态，这本质上是对苹果收费的再造。</p><p> “我们强烈敦促英国立法者迅速通过该法案，以阻止苹果实施类似的费用，这将有助于为英国消费者和企业创造一个更具竞争力和创新性的科技行业。”</p><p> Spotify 最近透露了自己的政策变化，要求<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-confirm-songs-now-need-at-least-1000-streams-to-earn-royalties-3546548#:~:text=Spotify%20confirm%20songs%20now%20need%20at%20least%201%2C000%20streams%20to%20earn%20royalties,-The%20new%20regulations&amp;text=Spotify%20have%20confirmed%20that%20all,they%20can%20earn%20any%20royalties.">平台上的所有歌曲至少拥有 1,000 条流媒体播放量，然后才能赚取版税</a>。</p><p>最近，欧盟<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/european-union-demands-streaming-services-increase-royalty-payments-to-artists-3573204">呼吁对流媒体业务进行变革</a>，要求向艺术家支付更高的版税，并“正确分配元数据”以使艺术家的作品更加可见。</p><p>该流媒体平台此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-to-cut-six-per-cent-of-workforce-3385265">于今年 1 月早些时候解雇了 6% 的员工</a>，当时表示这样做是为了提高“速度”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-announces-cut-of-1500-jobs-with-17-per-cent-of-workforce-facing-axe-3552871">上个月裁掉了 1,500 个工作岗位（占员工总数的 17%）</a> 。</p><p>首席执行官丹尼尔·埃克(Daniel Ek)表示，由于经济增长“急剧放缓”，他做出了“艰难”的决定。当时，Spotify 拥有约 9,000 名员工。</p><p> “我认识到这将影响许多做出了宝贵贡献的个人，”埃克写道。 “坦白说，许多聪明、有才华、勤奋的人将会离开我们。”他还补充说，裁员“对我们的团队来说将是极其痛苦的”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-slam-apples-outrageous-new-plans-and-accuse-them-of-stopping-at-nothing-to-protect-profits-3574954">Spotify 抨击苹果“令人发指”的新计划，并指责他们为保护利润“不择手段”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《WWE 2K24》揭晓，科迪·罗兹 (Cody Rhodes) 担任封面明星https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/wwe-2k24-revealed-with-cody-rhodes-as-the-cover-star-3574943?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=wwe-2k24-revealed-科迪·罗兹担任封面明星Ryan EasbyMon, 22 Jan 2024 14:44:26 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game CultureWWE https://www.nme.com/?p=3574943 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Cody-Rhodes.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《WWE 2K24》豪华版来源：2K" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Cody-Rhodes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Cody-Rhodes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Cody-Rhodes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Cody-Rhodes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Cody-Rhodes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Cody-Rhodes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该游戏预计将于三月推出</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/wwe-2k24-revealed-with-cody-rhodes-as-the-cover-star-3574943">由 Cody Rhodes 担任封面明星的《WWE 2K24》</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Cody-Rhodes.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《WWE 2K24》豪华版来源：2K" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Cody-Rhodes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Cody-Rhodes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Cody-Rhodes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Cody-Rhodes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Cody-Rhodes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Cody-Rhodes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>发行商 2K 和开发商 Visual Concepts 宣布，科迪·罗兹 (Cody Rhodes) 将成为<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/wwe">《WWE</a> 2K24》</em>的封面明星。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/the-last-of-us-part-2-remastered-review-3571657">《最后生还者第二部重制版》评论：令人沮丧，但值得</a></strong></li></ul><p>“众所周知，我会保留一份清单，列出我在完成故事的过程中想要经历的关键里程碑，”封面明星科迪·罗兹 (Cody Rhodes) 说道。</p><p> “作为一名狂热的游戏玩家，被评为<em>WWE 2K</em>封面超级巨星非常非常接近榜首，我很高兴与 2K 和 Visual Concepts 的团队合作，将这个梦想变为现实。”</p><p>与此同时，游戏的豪华版将庆祝该公司的女性摔跤手名单，封面人物是雷亚·里普利 (Rhea Ripley) 和比安卡·贝莱尔 (Bianca Belair)。</p><p> “这是我职业生涯中令人难以置信的里程碑，我很高兴向世界展示为什么<em>WWE 2K24</em>是每个 WWE 粉丝和游戏玩家的必备游戏和 EST 游戏，”Bianca Belair 说道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3574955" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3574955" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3574955" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Deluxe-Edition-Cover-Art.jpg" alt="《WWE 2K24》豪华版来源：2K" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Deluxe-Edition-Cover-Art.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Deluxe-Edition-Cover-Art-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Deluxe-Edition-Cover-Art-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Deluxe-Edition-Cover-Art-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Deluxe-Edition-Cover-Art-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/WWE-2K24-Deluxe-Edition-Cover-Art-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3574955" class="wp-caption-text"> 《WWE 2K24》豪华版来源：2K</figcaption></figure><p>与此同时，封面明星雷亚·里普利 (Rhea Ripley) 认为，她出现在封面上“非常合适”。</p><p> “我已经证明自己是 WWE 女子世界冠军史上最具统治力的竞争者。获得<em>《WWE 2K24》</em>封面《超级巨星》的荣誉是再合适不过了，我很自豪将其添加到我的成就清单中，”里普利说道</p><p>该游戏将于 3 月 8 日在全球发布，并采用新模式，通过展示摔跤历史上最具标志性时刻的关键事件和比赛来庆祝摔跤狂热 40 周年。</p><p>四种新的比赛类型也以特邀嘉宾裁判比赛（最后出现在<em>WWE 2K14</em>中）、救护车比赛（最后出现在<em>Raw vs Smackdown 2010 中）</em> 、棺材比赛（最后出现在<em>WWE 2K15 中）</em>和Gauntlet Match（最后出现在<em>WWE 2K14）。</em></p><p>该游戏的第一部预告片将在今晚的<em>周一晚上原始节目</em>中首映。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-legend-of-zelda">《塞尔达传说》</a></em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-legend-of-zelda-may-be-getting-its-own-lego-set-this-year-3574933">可能会在今年晚些时候推出自己的乐高套装</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/wwe-2k24-revealed-with-cody-rhodes-as-the-cover-star-3574943">由 Cody Rhodes 担任封面明星的《WWE 2K24》</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
